* should the GUI run not only for LAEs but for other objects too?

general comments:
    - pathlib offers useful classes for filesystem paths
    - "some text".format() is an easy and nice way to format the output
    - no need to wrap constants in arrays
    - using astropy Table allows to avoid e.g. input_cat_keys and input_cat_dict
    - fits.getdata(filename) is a fast way to get data from the first FITS hdu
    - using astropy SkyCoord for coordinate transormations